name: Ep. 126 - Arrival Deep Dive + Top Denis Villeneuve
summary: Ty Franck (one half of James S.A. Corey) and Wes Chatham ('Amos Burton' on The Expanse) decided after talking about Alien Invasions they wanted to do a deep dive on the movie Arrival. This is a book and a movie the guys both love so sit back and enjoy...
